articles.title: The Kitchen review: Daniel Kaluuya’s directorial debut is a stunner - The Verge
articles.description: Netflix’s The Kitchen from co-directors Kibwe Tavares and Daniel Kaluuya is a bleak, beautiful sci-fi vision of the future of housing inequality.
articles.content:
Co-directors Daniel Kaluuya and Kibwe Tavares new action drama is a masterclass in using near-futuristic, sci-fi storytelling to illustrate harsh realities about our present.
ByCharles Pulliam-Moore… [+6232 chars]
